 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">Freight selection is one of the largest variables in landed cost, often 15-30% of total. The right mode depends on order size, weight, and timeline. Below is a 2026 reference table based on average rates from Shenzhen to US, EU, and UK destinations, sourced from Freightos Baltic Index and our active forwarder relationships.</p>

